(window.webpackJsonp=window.webpackJsonp||[]).push([[44],{302:function(module,exports){module.exports={compilerOutput:[],storyContent:{inkVersion:19,root:[[{"->t->":"chapter_15_sound"},{"->t->":"chapter_15_start"},"ev","str","^","/str","/ev",{"->":"done"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{chapter_15_sound:['^<play-sound group="music" name="the-art-of-fortification" />',"\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":1}],chapter_15_start:["^<p>","\n","^Mother stands atop the grassy knoll of Carcassonne. Father is beside her. Below her on the hill are her proudest and most perfect children, and the Operating Group. Francis William Draaier kneels beneath Mother and Father, chained, bleeding, perfectly diminished.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^In the valley below are screams, hundreds of crosses, and a proudly Antediluvian crowd.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Each member of the crowd is crucified to each crossbeam.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Those who are crucified, below us in the fouled breeze, are selected from every stratum and schema of Antediluvian power, a sampler set of functionaries. An assorted medley of bureaucrats, security officers, secretaries, generals. Lions, cubs, officers of pride. Mad cats of every stripe, class, and clan.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^A volatile odor haunts the breeze, ancient death pressed into modern service. A miasma of loyal agents, prepared to be reborn at the slightest warm touch.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Mother begins the Word.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n",'^"What can we do about the Antediliuvian infinity war, the struggle session for the immortal and prodigal soul? Within infinity, one is always coming and going. <bdi>\u0915\u093e\u0932\u091a\u0915\u094d\u0930</bdi> is kinked and twisted around itself, so we pass endlessly over the same hills and valleys, the same curves and straightaways. Borne up and crushed under. Perpetually new and ever old."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Now Father speaks, and Mother is silent, watching.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^"If a million deaths is a statistic, then one death can only be a datum, nothing more. A billion is just one more recurrence of the nightmare from we cannot wake, all throughout the longest night. The soul can never die. So either it is mathematics in total, or all of it, as ever, shadowplay on cave walls."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>Now they are together, holding one other, speaking in matrimonial harmony. Or should that be harmonious matrimony?","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>Words fail the moment.</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^\"So let's do it right this time. Let's fix <bdi>\u1f41\u03bb\u03cc\u03ba\u03b1\u03c5\u03c3\u03c4\u03bf\u03c2</bdi>. Let's repair <bdi>\u0413\u043e\u043b\u043e\u0434\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0301\u0440</bdi>. Let's kick <bdi>\u5927\u8dc3\u8fdb</bdi> into overdrive and take every small step towards the most giant leap of all. Let's all dive into the deepest abyss. Let's produce \u0440\u0430\u0441\u043a\u0443\u043b\u0430\u0447\u0438\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 redux and let's go for the throne. If the Archon will always demand sacrifice, then let's make an offering of the whole world and burn it to nothing. Let's make a plague of hunger and every other hierarchical need. Let's collectivize everything and move everyone to the last commune.\"","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^\"Let's bite the feeding hand so hard we come away with tendons and bones. Let's punch up so hard the roof caves in. Let's bring a plague on every house. Let's transform every child, not just the first sons of our nearest enemies. Let's do everyone the favor of killing identities and politics. No borders means no egos. Free souls means no organs or bodies. Let's use up all the value, not just the surplus, and let's abstract every quantum of it. Let's take anger out of violence and replace it with love. It's not hatred if it's blind, and stoning the unjust is no sin for the perfect. Let's bring wormwood to every watershed. Let's bring mugwort to every commonwealth.\"","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^\"Let's burn the cathedral and the temples to the oaken forest gods, the palisades and the camps. Let's bring back the days of the locust and the days of fire. A just society gives the same to the meek and the complacent. So let's turn the flashbulbs up so high that each thing and its ashes look the same. Let's put our foot down and keep it off the brake. For our sake.\"","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^\"Let's plan the last five years, and the last five days. Let's attend to the transcendence of the eschaton. If the day of the rope will come, because it must, for reasons predestined at our birth; if we are to be given as failsafes the panoptic archipelago; caressing boots, doctors, and weasels with our loving tongues; kneeling reverently; or being trodden upon; if the only way off the rails is to be eviscerated by the locomotive of philosophy; then let's braid knots for every soul. Let's sign the DNR order for material existence and bring the human experiment to an end. The heroisch and euthanizing dose, the Mesopotamian consolamentum, administered to every immanent patient by galactic Kevorkians. What better zone than here? What truer cause than ours?\"","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n",'^"No cosmic weapon will form against us now. At last, we will transform every <bdi>\u03b3\u03ad\u03bd\u03bf\u03c2</bdi>, and it will be good. From us according to our ability, to each for their need."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Mother is nearly screaming now, the rawness in her voice plain.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^"<em>Ardua pennis astra sequi</em>; <em>est ad astra mollis e terris via</em>; <em>sic itur ad astra</em>. Then we put out every star. Finally it is, at worst, <strong>milk all the way</strong>."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Father steps down the gentle curve of the hill. He speaks out, towards the prisoners, and upwards.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^"So if it may be that there are good souls among them, willing to turn their cheek to evil, then let the Archon sort them himself. Until then let them burn."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Father raises one hand in salute. In the other he holds a grenade launcher, stout, bulbous, tapered. He speaks with incredible force.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^"This offering is for our most high Archon. We have provided a sacrifice of the fattest and youngest cubs of the Capital Zone. Let its sweet fumes rise to His highest offices. Let Him be pleased by our sacrifice."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Mother, at her last shouted zenith:","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^"This is how rats skin cats. This is how your Mother measures twice and cuts once. This is what becomes of the Terran babe, the Omelasian world, which all low mothers of Malkuth neither gave up nor shared in community. Watch it now split into infinite portions. Watch it distribute with perfect equity, all the way up to Kether."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^A hollow report, like a half-empty can hitting the floor, and the shell is free.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^"And let there be only created light."',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^The grenade soars towards its apex, hanging as if suspended by wires. It turns downward to face its quarry, proud and uniformed lions, bound and gagged, whimpering for their false father. Faster and faster towards the final instant of purpose.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Detonation. A screaming comes across the plain. High and sourceless, a typhoon of pain and prayer, it moves through us all, divine lightning.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^A plume of flame erupts on the fuel-soaked earth, reaching to embrace each of the crucified Antediluvians. Thunder of the divine Mother comes as shock front. A signal fire bursts forth, a bright semaphore to warn the heavens, from under a cloudless sky.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Francis William Draaier rises. Mother unlocks his handcuffs; Father removes his ball and chain. He makes a sign of reverence, closes his eyes.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^He speaks, for the first time I can recall since we filmed his dire confession.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n",'^"<strong>Death to the Archon. And death to the sinner known as Francis William Draaier.</strong>"',"\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Francis William Draaier runs to the flames.","\n","^</p>","\n",["ev",{"VAR?":"chapter_13_broke_draaiers_ribs"},"/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["\n","^<p>","\n","^As he goes, my eyes meet with his a final time.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^I've never seen such fear in my life. He looks like a horse, chased down to exhaustion, spitting and kicking to keep me away for a few final seconds, howling his last...","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Did I do this?","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Did I somehow initiate <em>all</em> this?","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.216"},null]}],"nop","\n","^<p>","\n","^Draaier is transformed by the fire.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n","^Cheers and shouts. A band begins to play in the Perfect crowd. The rhythm of death grooves with heartbeat and love. The key is D minor and the mode Lydian. The mood is Delphic.","\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^Keep from our brush-filled high-topped slopes, O Lions, from our faded and oozing citadel, Parnassos of the Albigensian Middle East, ridges blue and endless into the horizon. Sinners are no longer welcome. There is no one left to lead the campaigns of revanche, no dancers, no martial drummers. No more kings, no more gods.","\n","^</p>","\n",{"->t->":"yield"},"^<p>","\n",'^Antediluvian tulips burst forth where depravity lay fallow. We told them, "Do not visit that preterite zone." Now we have shown them why. Pain as community, community through pain. And fire for all those who refuse.',"\n","^</p>","\n","^<p>","\n","^We have won the end.","\n","^</p>","\n","ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":1}],yield:[["ev","str","^\u25fc","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0",flg:4},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["ev","void","/ev","->->",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],done:[{"temp=":"out_var"},[["ev",{"VAR?":"out_var"},"/ev",{"->":".^.b",c:!0},{b:["\n","ev",{"VAR?":"out_var"},"/ev",{"VAR=":"XLR8R_OUT_PASSAGE",re:!0},{"->":"done.1.1"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev","str","^\u25fc","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0",flg:20},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":['^<stop-sound group="music" name="the-art-of-fortification" />',"\n","done",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"global decl":["ev","str","^XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE","/str",{"VAR=":"DEBUG"},"str","^chapter-16","/str",{"VAR=":"XLR8R_OUT_PASSAGE"},"str","^XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE","/str",{"VAR=":"XLR8R_NEW_GAME"},"str","^XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE","/str",{"VAR=":"chapter_13_broke_draaiers_ribs"},"/ev","end",null],"#f":1}],listDefs:{}},text:'VAR DEBUG = "XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE"\r\n\r\nVAR XLR8R_OUT_PASSAGE = "chapter-16"\r\n\r\nVAR XLR8R_NEW_GAME = "XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE"\r\n\r\n\r\nVAR chapter_13_broke_draaiers_ribs = "XLR8R_PREVIOUS_VALUE"\r\n\r\n\r\n-> chapter_15_sound ->\r\n\r\n-> chapter_15_start ->\r\n\r\n-> done("")\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_15_sound ===\r\n<play-sound group="music" name="the-art-of-fortification" />\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== chapter_15_start ===\r\n<p>\r\nMother stands atop the grassy knoll of Carcassonne. Father is beside her. Below her on the hill are her proudest and most perfect children, and the Operating Group. Francis William Draaier kneels beneath Mother and Father, chained, bleeding, perfectly diminished.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nIn the valley below are screams, hundreds of crosses, and a proudly Antediluvian crowd.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nEach member of the crowd is crucified to each crossbeam.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThose who are crucified, below us in the fouled breeze, are selected from every stratum and schema of Antediluvian power, a sampler set of functionaries. An assorted medley of bureaucrats, security officers, secretaries, generals. Lions, cubs, officers of pride. Mad cats of every stripe, class, and clan.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nA volatile odor haunts the breeze, ancient death pressed into modern service. A miasma of loyal agents, prepared to be reborn at the slightest warm touch.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nMother begins the Word.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"What can we do about the Antediliuvian infinity war, the struggle session for the immortal and prodigal soul? Within infinity, one is always coming and going. <bdi>\u0915\u093e\u0932\u091a\u0915\u094d\u0930</bdi> is kinked and twisted around itself, so we pass endlessly over the same hills and valleys, the same curves and straightaways. Borne up and crushed under. Perpetually new and ever old."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nNow Father speaks, and Mother is silent, watching.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"If a million deaths is a statistic, then one death can only be a datum, nothing more. A billion is just one more recurrence of the nightmare from we cannot wake, all throughout the longest night. The soul can never die. So either it is mathematics in total, or all of it, as ever, shadowplay on cave walls."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>Now they are together, holding one other, speaking in matrimonial harmony. Or should that be harmonious matrimony?\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Words fail the moment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"So let\'s do it right this time. Let\'s fix <bdi>\u1f41\u03bb\u03cc\u03ba\u03b1\u03c5\u03c3\u03c4\u03bf\u03c2</bdi>. Let\'s repair <bdi>\u0413\u043e\u043b\u043e\u0434\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0301\u0440</bdi>. Let\'s kick <bdi>\u5927\u8dc3\u8fdb</bdi> into overdrive and take every small step towards the most giant leap of all. Let\'s all dive into the deepest abyss. Let\'s produce \u0440\u0430\u0441\u043a\u0443\u043b\u0430\u0447\u0438\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 redux and let\'s go for the throne. If the Archon will always demand sacrifice, then let\'s make an offering of the whole world and burn it to nothing. Let\'s make a plague of hunger and every other hierarchical need. Let\'s collectivize everything and move everyone to the last commune."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"Let\'s bite the feeding hand so hard we come away with tendons and bones. Let\'s punch up so hard the roof caves in. Let\'s bring a plague on every house. Let\'s transform every child, not just the first sons of our nearest enemies. Let\'s do everyone the favor of killing identities and politics. No borders means no egos. Free souls means no organs or bodies. Let\'s use up all the value, not just the surplus, and let\'s abstract every quantum of it. Let\'s take anger out of violence and replace it with love. It\'s not hatred if it\'s blind, and stoning the unjust is no sin for the perfect. Let\'s bring wormwood to every watershed. Let\'s bring mugwort to every commonwealth."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"Let\'s burn the cathedral and the temples to the oaken forest gods, the palisades and the camps. Let\'s bring back the days of the locust and the days of fire. A just society gives the same to the meek and the complacent. So let\'s turn the flashbulbs up so high that each thing and its ashes look the same. Let\'s put our foot down and keep it off the brake. For our sake."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"Let\'s plan the last five years, and the last five days. Let\'s attend to the transcendence of the eschaton. If the day of the rope will come, because it must, for reasons predestined at our birth; if we are to be given as failsafes the panoptic archipelago; caressing boots, doctors, and weasels with our loving tongues; kneeling reverently; or being trodden upon; if the only way off the rails is to be eviscerated by the locomotive of philosophy; then let\'s braid knots for every soul. Let\'s sign the DNR order for material existence and bring the human experiment to an end. The heroisch and euthanizing dose, the Mesopotamian consolamentum, administered to every immanent patient by galactic Kevorkians. What better zone than here? What truer cause than ours?"\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"No cosmic weapon will form against us now. At last, we will transform every <bdi>\u03b3\u03ad\u03bd\u03bf\u03c2</bdi>, and it will be good. From us according to our ability, to each for their need."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nMother is nearly screaming now, the rawness in her voice plain.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"<em>Ardua pennis astra sequi</em>; <em>est ad astra mollis e terris via</em>; <em>sic itur ad astra</em>. Then we put out every star. Finally it is, at worst, <strong>milk all the way</strong>."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFather steps down the gentle curve of the hill. He speaks out, towards the prisoners, and upwards.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"So if it may be that there are good souls among them, willing to turn their cheek to evil, then let the Archon sort them himself. Until then let them burn."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFather raises one hand in salute. In the other he holds a grenade launcher, stout, bulbous, tapered. He speaks with incredible force.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"This offering is for our most high Archon. We have provided a sacrifice of the fattest and youngest cubs of the Capital Zone. Let its sweet fumes rise to His highest offices. Let Him be pleased by our sacrifice."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nMother, at her last shouted zenith:\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"This is how rats skin cats. This is how your Mother measures twice and cuts once. This is what becomes of the Terran babe, the Omelasian world, which all low mothers of Malkuth neither gave up nor shared in community. Watch it now split into infinite portions. Watch it distribute with perfect equity, all the way up to Kether."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nA hollow report, like a half-empty can hitting the floor, and the shell is free.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"And let there be only created light."\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nThe grenade soars towards its apex, hanging as if suspended by wires. It turns downward to face its quarry, proud and uniformed lions, bound and gagged, whimpering for their false father. Faster and faster towards the final instant of purpose.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nDetonation. A screaming comes across the plain. High and sourceless, a typhoon of pain and prayer, it moves through us all, divine lightning.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nA plume of flame erupts on the fuel-soaked earth, reaching to embrace each of the crucified Antediluvians. Thunder of the divine Mother comes as shock front. A signal fire bursts forth, a bright semaphore to warn the heavens, from under a cloudless sky.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFrancis William Draaier rises. Mother unlocks his handcuffs; Father removes his ball and chain. He makes a sign of reverence, closes his eyes.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nHe speaks, for the first time I can recall since we filmed his dire confession.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n"<strong>Death to the Archon. And death to the sinner known as Francis William Draaier.</strong>"\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFrancis William Draaier runs to the flames.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n{\r\n    - chapter_13_broke_draaiers_ribs:\r\n        <p>\r\n        As he goes, my eyes meet with his a final time. \r\n        </p>\r\n\r\n        <p>\r\n        I\'ve never seen such fear in my life. He looks like a horse, chased down to exhaustion, spitting and kicking to keep me away for a few final seconds, howling his last...\r\n        </p>\r\n\r\n        <p>\r\n        Did I do this?\r\n        </p>\r\n\r\n        <p>\r\n        Did I somehow initiate <em>all</em> this?\r\n        </p>\r\n}\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nDraaier is transformed by the fire.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nCheers and shouts. A band begins to play in the Perfect crowd. The rhythm of death grooves with heartbeat and love. The key is D minor and the mode Lydian. The mood is Delphic.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nKeep from our brush-filled high-topped slopes, O Lions, from our faded and oozing citadel, Parnassos of the Albigensian Middle East, ridges blue and endless into the horizon. Sinners are no longer welcome. There is no one left to lead the campaigns of revanche, no dancers, no martial drummers. No more kings, no more gods.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n-> yield ->\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nAntediluvian tulips burst forth where depravity lay fallow. We told them, "Do not visit that preterite zone." Now we have shown them why. Pain as community, community through pain. And fire for all those who refuse.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe have won the end.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== yield ===\r\n+ [\u25fc]\r\n-\r\n\r\n->->\r\n\r\n\r\n=== done(out_var) ===\r\n{\r\n    - out_var:\r\n        ~ XLR8R_OUT_PASSAGE = out_var\r\n}\r\n\r\n* [\u25fc]\r\n-\r\n\r\n<stop-sound group="music" name="the-art-of-fortification" />\r\n\r\n-> DONE'}}}]);